The,Word,Cloud,API,allow,the,user,to,create,word,clouds,based,on,text,input,either,as,a,block,of,text,or,an,array,of,words,and,importance,The,word,clouds,can,be,customized,through,a,range,of,options,including,size,language,colors,and,more,This,API,has,one,free,plan,and,two,paid,plans,Basic,requests,a,month,free,overage,Pro,requests,per,month,and,Ultra,unlimited,requests